query:
SELECT pwi.id, pwi.productId, pwi.productSku, pwi.batch, p.sku 
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
JOIN products p ON pwi.productId = p.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = 3 AND pwi.productSku = '834207';
